templateVersions.content:
Summarize this student's application in simple, plain-language terms. Include: - Student name: {!$Input:Student_Enrollment__c.Student__r.LastName}
Course applied: {!$Input:Student_Enrollment__c.Course__r.Name}
Course fee and discount: {!$Input:Student_Enrollment__c.Course__r.Course_Fee__c} with a discount of {!$Input:Student_Enrollment__c.Discount_Percentage__c}
- Final payable amount: {!$Input:Student_Enrollment__c.Final_Payable_Amount__c}
- Enrollment status: {!$Input:Student_Enrollment__c.Enrollment_Status__c}
- AI priority score: {!$Input:Student_Enrollment__c.AI_Priority_Score__c}
Then highlight any risks or special considerations a counselor should be aware of.
